================================================================================
Third-party components fetched at build time (NOT included in this repository)
================================================================================

No third-party code is redistributed in this repository. The build fetches it:

  ZMK Firmware   MIT          https://github.com/zmkfirmware/zmk
  Zephyr RTOS    Apache-2.0   https://github.com/zephyrproject-rtos/zephyr
  MCUboot        Apache-2.0   https://github.com/mcu-tools/mcuboot
  hal_telink     Apache-2.0   https://github.com/telink-semi/hal_telink
    (the above are fetched by `west`, per zmk/west.yml)

  Telink B91 Bluetooth LE controller library — liblt_9518_zephyr.a
    Source:    https://github.com/telink-semi/zephyr_hal_telink_b91_ble_lib
    Copyright (c) Telink Semiconductor (Shanghai) Co., Ltd.
    License:   PROPRIETARY — confidential, non-transferable, granted under NDA;
               NOT redistributable. This repository therefore does NOT contain
               the blob. `fetch_ble_blob.sh` downloads it at build time (pinned
               commit + SHA-256 verified) from Telink's own public repository,
               and links it unmodified.

